---
description: Ping NotchPill when the agent finishes a reply.
alwaysApply: true
---

**Every time you finish a reply**, run this as your **last shell command**:

```bash
./Scripts/notify-notchpill.sh "Short title" "What you finished or answered" Cursor com.todesktop.230313mzl4w4u92 "YOUR_MODEL_NAME"
```

Also queue for the stop hook backup:

```bash
./Scripts/queue-notchpill-notify.sh "Short title" "What you finished" Cursor com.todesktop.230313mzl4w4u92 "YOUR_MODEL_NAME"
```

Always notify — including short answers. Use your real model name for the badge.
